snippet.title: Edge of Eternity - Console release date trailer
snippet.description:
📢This end of the year has been rich in revelations 🥳

Edge of Eternity will be available:
- On PS4|5 & Xbox One|Series on February 10th
- Japanese voices will be integrated on February 10th for PC & Console versions
- on Switch in Cloud version on February 23rd  with Ubitus

All the links: https://linktr.ee/edgeofeternity
